Subject: Re: [VB] Oil opinions

> What do people think about using 10-30 or 20-50 oil?

For some reason, I use Castrol 30 or Castrol 20W-50,
but I don't know why.  I always used Pennzoil 30 in my
water cooled vehicles, but nothing I own is water
cooled anymore.

For years I wouldn't use any multigrade oils - just
didn't trust the additive package, I suppose.

